:{"pid":"8ba8216a0c2706e830bd2e66356b8b654ac09e0c","tid":1289357,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"屌，共產黨鳩嗡呃廢老既外國勢力論呃埋呢個廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:50:05.000Z","msg":"佢無咩高見，只係傳聲筒"},{"pid":"8cb52f1f08f421f70ccaadc00e3126bea2bb586c","tid":1289357,"uid":76591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"好記得佢當年係中央政策組首席顧問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得老董咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6c313f82180fab7e7782cb78442dab8fedf6ea","tid":1289357,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:55:14.000Z","msg":"啲思維同廢老無分別"},{"pid":"94ef0e47f742d689f4f318455dd00b0cedb150e0","tid":1289357,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"政治生涯\t<br />\n編輯<br />\n<br />\n除教學及研究外，劉兆佳一直積極參政，於1993年獲中央政府委任為港事顧問，同年獲全國人民代表大會常務委員會委任為香港特區籌委會預委會委員，1996年接續獲委任為香港特區籌委會委員，2003年起獲委任中國人民政治協商會議全國委員會委員。2002年至2012年出任香港特區政府中央政策組首席顧問。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳加入政府前經常在報章撰文，對香港政制發展發表意見，對政府及政策作出批評，但2002年加入政府後，劉兆佳表示在集體負責制下，以維護政府的權威和政策，就公開發言對自己設下「四不」政策，即不評論北京政策、不評論其他個別官員言論、不與政府唱對台戲及不反對特區政府政策[3]。其言論作風的轉變，為部份學者所詬病[4]。劉兆佳初加入政府時曾表示只是短期參與，原大學教職務停薪留職[5]，三年任期完結後會返回香港中文大學任教[4]，2005年延任兩年至當屆政府任期完結[6]，2007年繼續留任新屆政府[7]，同年正式自香港中文大學退休，2012年隨當屆政府任期完結離任。"},{"pid":"782293ea2e43986fa2821932bf147751d5eb0920","tid":1289357,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8cb52f1f08f421f70ccaadc00e3126bea2bb586c","tid":1289357,"uid":76591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"好記得佢當年係中央政策組首席顧問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得老董咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"呢條廢柴有份助攻令老董提早下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcaf302a664bad4448c56362f01023be55a4199e","tid":1289357,"uid":39021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔洗再理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢講D野伏到自己友都唔理佢"},{"pid":"f6bd1a92c4546ddaae243da5c975f5e79c4058f5","tid":1289357,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcaf302a664bad4448c56362f01023be55a4199e","tid":1289357,"uid":39021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔洗再理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢講D野伏到自己友都唔理佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"大把傳媒訪問佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed84b3b3911b254493f783a5418e4b1641445741","tid":1289357,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}